    public class Arrow
extends AbstractSilhouette

    Arrow

    Defines an arrow shape

    Constraints

    1. 0 <= depth <= 1

    2. 0 <= rise <= 1

    Style Classes

    1. silhouette

    2. silhouette-arrow
